Instalation:

1. Download Go compiler
2. tar -zxvf go1.2.linux-amd64.tar.gz
3. Set path to GOROOT, like: export GOROOT=/home/kkszysiu/go/go
4. export GOPATH=/home/kkszysiu/go/powerline-shell-go/
5. /home/kkszysiu/go/go/bin/go get
6. /home/kkszysiu/go/go/bin/go build
7. Open ~/.bashrc
8. Add 


```
#!bash

# powerline-shell-go
function _update_ps1() {
    export PS1="$(~/bin/powerline-shell-go/powerline-shell-go $?)"
}
export PROMPT_COMMAND="_update_ps1"

```

9. ???
10. PROFIT